<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>404 — ページが見つかりません | Koe Device</title>
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0f1a">
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
body{font-family:-apple-system,'Helvetica Neue','Hiragino Sans',sans-serif;
  background:#07090f;color:#f1f5f9;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;min-height:100vh;text-align:center;padding:2rem}
.wrap{max-width:480px}
.code{font-size:7rem;font-weight:100;letter-spacing:-0.04em;color:#1f2937;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1rem}
h1{font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:0.6rem}
p{color:#64748b;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:2rem}
.links{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.6rem;justify-content:center}
a{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.3rem;padding:0.6rem 1.2rem;border-radius:9px;
  font-size:0.82rem;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);color:#f1f5f9;text-decoration:none;
  transition:border-color 0.2s}
a:hover{border-color:rgba(16,185,129,0.4);color:#10B981}
a.home{background:#10B981;color:#000;border-color:transparent}
a.home:hover{opacity:0.88}
</style>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/koe-nav.css">
  <script src="/assets/koe-nav.js" defer></script>
  <script defer src="https://enabler-analytics.fly.dev/t.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="koe-with-nav">
<div id="koe-nav"></div>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="code">404</div>
  <h1><span class="ja">ページが見つかりません</span><span class="en">Page not found</span></h1>
  <p><span class="ja">お探しのページは移動・削除されたか、URLが間違っている可能性があります。</span><span class="en">The page you're looking for may have moved, been removed, or the URL might be incorrect.</span></p>
  <div class="links">
    <a href="/" class="home">← <span class="ja">トップへ</span><span class="en">Home</span></a>
    <a href="/products"><span class="ja">製品一覧</span><span class="en">Products</span></a>
    <a href="/status"><span class="ja">ステータス</span><span class="en">Status</span></a>
    <a href="/coin">COIN</a>
    <a href="/guide">GUIDE</a>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
